summary:
A Bachelor graduate in International Business at Fontys University of Applied Sciences, The Netherlands. Diversified knowledge covering Data Analytics, Supply Chain, Finances and Logistics. Well-versed in data research, analysis, visualization, and strategic planning skills developed throughout the work experiences and university group projects. Additionally, coupled with an advanced understanding of Excel and Microsoft Office’s Products and Tools.

“If you’ve failed, that means you’re doing something. If you’re doing something, you have a chance.” - Robert Kiyosaki
